Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.98,0:00:06.94,Signs_WText,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(521,1)\an7\bord0.6\pos(693,793.5)}第12话   平时是什么样的来着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:13.45,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:14.13,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:14.87,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:17.13,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叶香乘上了那辆电车！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:18.87,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.63,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香被带走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:41.54,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,毒太郎似乎要不择手段地带走叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:43.26,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,因为她是7G的钥匙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.26,0:00:44.92,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这样啊！所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:46.28,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,把叶香带回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:51.57,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果叶香自己想走的话暂且不论
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:53.89,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,强行带她走的话绝对不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:55.12,Default,Group,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:01.57,Default,Leader,0,0,0,,别让他们跑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:03.91,Default,Leader,0,0,0,,她们逃掉我们就要变茶碗蒸了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.95,0:01:06.81,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 是诚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:07.69,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,呀吼～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:09.21,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,毒太郎逃走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:11.52,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,按钮怎么样了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:13.53,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,虽然被藏在奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:15.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是按了却什么反应也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:17.18,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不行！要追他的话 就带着走！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.78,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,比起这个 叶香的事更重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.78,0:01:21.49,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,回去拿太麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:22.79,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,{\an8}你们的目的是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:24.47,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,夺回叶香？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:24.99,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.99,0:01:27.16,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,还有把世界恢复原状？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:29.04,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这个嘛 也有吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:31.75,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,毒太郎只是自作聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:33.14,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,他的行动很单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:34.83,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,就是因为那个重要他才会藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:35.42,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:36.21,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,以及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:40.05,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,这么重要的按钮他却因为急着逃跑所以没带上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.91,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,不要 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:44.70,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:45.74,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:47.41,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,您没必要如此担心！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:48.99,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,有我在很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:51.57,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,担心？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:55.09,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就是 那群蛮不讲理之徒 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:56.07,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,蛮不讲理…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:56.94,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,对的对的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:59.49,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,她们意图危害公主您的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:01.10,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,但是请安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:04.60,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,本人毒太郎必会全心全意竭尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.34,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,那么 我去确认情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:10.37,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,还请公主您像平时一样度过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.44,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,像平时一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.64,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,平时是什么样的来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:18.68,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,睡觉 起床 吃饭 学习…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:21.61,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,除此之外…还有谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.03,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,刚刚的是什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:26.48,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,波奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:27.99,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,快来！不在吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.53,0:02:31.10,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,所以那个按钮有意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:32.02,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,意义…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:34.38,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,可能是某种特别的按钮吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:37.35,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,或者除了启动7G以外就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.93,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就是说必须叶香和按钮两者都在的意思吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:43.15,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啊这样！是一套的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:43.96,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:48.06,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,所以她在那被叫作「池袋的魔女」是有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.68,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就是说 叶香按了按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.11,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,按钮赋予了叶香力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.64,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,然后世界就被改变了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 好聪明！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:57.17,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,肯定就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:58.08,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:00.38,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,按下按钮的必须是同一…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.32,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,让按下按钮的中富叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.36,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,再次按下按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:10.90,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,这恐怕是让叶香和世界变回来的唯一方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.05,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哦 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.57,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 路分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:37.66,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 该走哪条路好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:40.08,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:42.53,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶诶诶？波奇你认得路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不愧是波奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:53.74,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,最近诸事不利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:57.21,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,她不老老实实地当个人偶的话我会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:09.55,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.23,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,难缠的家伙们！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:12.58,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是我 你人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:13.53,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,赶快过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.22,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.52,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:06.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:07.43,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}不行啊 她完全听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.35,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,烦人的家伙们！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.07,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,怎么能把公主交给你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.03,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.32,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,决定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:57.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.17,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要到那辆列车上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:05:59.63,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.45,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但但但是 怎么去？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也去！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:02.88,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:03.77,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:04.24,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啥？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.14,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:11.75,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:15.50,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,万一回到常态的话 我会被追究7G的责任的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.15,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这种事绝对不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.69,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,啊！终于来了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.82,Default,Chaos,0,0,0,,毁了我国的大罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.76,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,给我赔偿啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:28.11,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,碍事！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.84,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,变成骨头吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,碍事！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.42,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,没用的家伙们！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.26,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:04.63,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,打中的话会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:05.40,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,蠢货吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.75,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我就是要你们死！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:07.39,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.78,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,要我们死的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:09.53,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.76,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你们对公主什么都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.13,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,池袋和公主同在！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:16.65,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,无公主 无池袋！无池袋 无公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:18.59,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:27.65,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:28.47,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.81,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,把这群家伙干掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.09,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,有个问题要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:37.73,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,「无池袋 无公主」是说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:39.90,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.72,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,以池袋为中心的7G能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:45.11,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是以她为中心产生的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.07,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,她和池袋是共生关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.41,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,池袋因她而生 她也因池袋而生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:51.40,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:52.03,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}诶？诶？诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.22,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嘘！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:54.45,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,要消耗叶香大人的生命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.20,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,消耗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.07,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.86,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,人终有一死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:08:01.05,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,为维持池袋的伟业献上生命有什么不满的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.93,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,其中有叶香大人的意志吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:05.83,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你是不是误会了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.62,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你只是个保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:10.26,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我是叶香大人的保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.16,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,不是你的保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:13.01,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:16.46,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,叶香大人是因为7G才痛苦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:17.79,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是又怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:20.68,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,停下7G 她的痛苦就能够结束吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:21.65,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.99,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,7G创造了作为魔女的叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.22,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,而叶香创造了7G的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:26.72,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,按钮！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:27.43,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,原来如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:28.31,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,按下按钮的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.88,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你这乌鸦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:38.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:40.46,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,叶香大人就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:44.02,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是不与我们为敌的意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.89,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,和叶香相关的话 就是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:49.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,可以这么理解吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.13,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.14,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,叶香大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:04.94,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.26,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,请用茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:07.51,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:21.07,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:21.92,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,应该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.67,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香肯定也明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:28.70,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不懂的话 给她看这本《练爱》肯定就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.47,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,她读点涩龙的话可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.20,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.71,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,哦 是香桃木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:36.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,和叶香没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.50,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:38.43,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,为什么要带过来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:41.68,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.19,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香说这花和星星一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:45.30,Default,Group,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:46.06,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:48.45,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,很久以前 在学校菜园
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.44,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:53.18,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叶香从那时起就在想星星的事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:55.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香 认得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:57.03,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是我啊 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.15,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,静留…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.33,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你忘了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.68,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,记不起来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:03.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:06.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我不是来寻求你的谅解的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.66,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最差…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,与其说是最差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你不原谅我也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:14.40,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,只是 我只是想对伤害了你而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.00,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:18.83,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留基本上吐不出象牙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:20.56,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,听着就尴尬！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这不是我真正的心情！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.64,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不对 稍微有点是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:26.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个啊 我不是笨蛋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.49,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,因为是笨蛋所以你比我厉害得多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:33.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你越厉害 我就越自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以我才故意说了难听的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.33,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 就算说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:40.72,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我自己还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.28,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我现在明白了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.64,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:56.97,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香生气是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.03,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:05.84,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香 别这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:08.73,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,为什么叶香要攻击静留啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.64,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我不懂啊叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:15.99,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,不要…这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.39,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,想…你想起来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:24.71,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,「说到底叶香你是不可能的」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:27.70,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,「说这种大话不会害羞吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:31.37,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,「我不管你了啊叶香」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.72,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,别说了啊叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.53,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,怪吓人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:36.51,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:38.85,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,是你说过的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:40.00,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:44.06,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然说了 但只是不想你离开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.47,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,现在…现在的话我清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.78,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我明白的！我清楚！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:51.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「反正肯定不行」是多伤人的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.87,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但那时我不是为了伤害你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:56.00,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也不是为了嘲笑你才说的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:59.86,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,所以你才从吾野来把我带回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.15,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想为我曾说过的话道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:06.03,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,而且我还想告诉你 我会相信叶香的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:09.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,想要支持你 想要为你应援！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:12.49,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,满口都是自己的主张 你真是傲慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:13.11,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:13.90,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:14.81,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你说得太过了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:16.59,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香 你说错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:19.21,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我觉得静留确实说了很过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:23.11,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但如果只是因为傲慢\N怎么会在这两年间始终如一地寻找你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.87,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,又怎么会来池袋呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.84,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,对呀 一路上很不容易的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:28.66,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我又没求着你们来 那也跟我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.38,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对 没求着我们来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:33.61,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是如果你仍要拒绝\N那你永远都只能这样一成不变了呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:34.84,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,一成不变…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:38.63,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我以前也一直认为 一成不变就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:42.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一直待在吾野 和叶香 和大家在一起就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:45.10,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以我起初只是想要把叶香带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:48.02,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但我现在终于明白 那样就太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:51.01,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果能看到未来和结果 那该多无聊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:54.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,未知的 无法理解的事物越多 才会越有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:59.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我们从吾野来到池袋\N一路上真的发生了很多不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.26,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是也很好玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.75,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,尽是些在吾野不可能遇上的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.75,0:13:06.70,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是啊 现在世界却不再变化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.25,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,已经处于停滞之中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:09.41,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,甚至更糟！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:10.86,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,好像还在缩小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:13.55,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想要作出改变 也想让世界发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.19,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香你其实也是——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:17.64,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:18.14,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.87,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,不要擅自断定我想要什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:28.69,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:33.04,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.29,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你现在觉得开心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:44.17,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,不开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.51,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:20.33,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然在吾野发生了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:23.87,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有伤心的事情 痛苦的事情\N甚至是当时觉得天塌地陷的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:27.06,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 过去的种种回忆 我都觉得十分开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.46,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香你还有梦想不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:31.80,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,虽然现在无从着手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:34.83,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但如果世界恢复原样 说不定就能实现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.61,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你就可以为此付出努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.15,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就存在可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:39.86,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,可能性…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:40.89,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:42.93,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,让世界再次运转起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.81,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.37,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,如果做不到 就会很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:53.10,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果无法实现 就会很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:56.20,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是我会为叶香应援的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.11,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:59.57,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,会超努力为你应援 给你加油的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:04.01,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,比起什么都不做而后悔\N付诸行动之后 就算后悔也完全可以接受！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.55,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以我会为你应援！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:12.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那是天狼星！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:13.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,天狼星？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:16.03,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,约定之星…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:23.03,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,向那闪耀的约定之星起誓吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.47,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,约定之星？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:26.07,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我刚刚给它取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.61,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,它的名字不是「天狼星」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:31.72,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那就把那个作为我们独有的称呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:32.61,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.54,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我没有让你应援的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.43,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:46.82,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我曾经瞧不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:49.35,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,觉得你满口大话却一事无成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.51,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,根本没有可能达成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:56.08,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,瞧不起你\N觉得你就这么永远停滞不前 腐朽堕落就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:57.05,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,暗自嘲笑过你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.22,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,诅咒过你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.03,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那才不是诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.52,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那是愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.48,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:09.82,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,因为 无论我最终留在吾野 或是去往别处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:13.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你都会想着我 我很高兴呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:18.00,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,静留你真是个笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:20.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂 叶香呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:23.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,比起独自待在这里 还是跟大家在一起更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:24.28,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这样绝对会更有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:29.14,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,以后的事情 就到那时那地再思考
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:52.44,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:54.32,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.53,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我可不会让你们得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:08.59,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:09.22,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:15.99,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:19.51,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,吓了我一跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.13,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:22.42,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,真是意想不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.88,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那不是魔女公主吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:25.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她是叶香啦 中富叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.76,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,原来如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:34.31,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,如果世界恢复原样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:36.58,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,即使世界无法恢复原样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:37.94,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那就到时候再想办法！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.34,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,乐观主义！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:40.71,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那样不也挺好的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:00.72,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,叶香大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.17,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这是 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.03,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:30.96,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋原来是这样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:30.96,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你们看那边！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:33.42,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,感觉是这样 又感觉好像不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.79,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香倒是跟以前一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:35.40,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.51,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.60,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:40.52,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯 百分之百变回了我们认识的叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:41.33,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:44.40,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,感觉跟原来不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.40,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.84,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,即使河流看似一如既往地流动着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:50.38,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,其中的水也会发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.87,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,无论是城市 还是人 就连世界也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:54.72,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,看似一样 实则有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:55.99,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,都在不断变化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:59.19,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,没想到你会说这么帅气的总结台词…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:01.40,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,世界无法恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:02.89,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,它将会继续变化下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:03.45,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:08.49,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,让我再次去见证这个世界吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:10.66,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,有缘再见！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.30,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,诶？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:20.32,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,感谢或是赞赏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:22.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,其中之一 又或者两者皆有？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:24.31,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,可是大家明明都变回人类了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:25.63,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,并不是变回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:29.27,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而是曾为人类的僵尸\N又变成了新的人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.17,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:32.43,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我还是你们的女王吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:37.57,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 你还真是适合坐在王座上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.82,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,黑木木！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.37,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你们接下来有什么打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:44.33,Default,Group,0,0,0,,回吾野！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:51.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,目标确定！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:53.44,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,远地点号 出发前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.44,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,远地点号？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:04.42,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这是静留起的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.62,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:09.32,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野现在怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:11.50,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不应该是「变成怎样了呢」吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:19.68,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:20.40,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:22.98,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,哦 我知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:23.66,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(189,1)\blur0.6\fscx90\fs48\fnCourier New\c&H274B46&\frz0.6755\fax0.05\pos(972,489)}来电呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:25.01,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,接通了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:27.67,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,果然是因为你们把7G停下来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:28.17,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,你问这边？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.14,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.41,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,这边同时发生着 让人高兴的事情\N以及并非如此的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.09,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,或者说 难以评判的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.74,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,我不会说一切影响都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:39.84,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,仍有一些 不 很多影响遗留了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:40.72,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,善治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.37,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,记录下所有人的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:42.97,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:45.33,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,大诚老师真会使唤人——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:48.68,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:52.53,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,今天的反帽帽模式比昨天延长了39秒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:53.92,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,总之 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.44,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,回来的路上也小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.91,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,说不定会比去的时候还要艰难
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:03.09,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:03.74,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:04.81,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,有什么东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.56,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,别的路线？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:07.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.69,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,莫非是西武新宿线？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:10.35,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,它回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.62,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们也回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.00,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的「回来」了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.49,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,说不定那是新的 未知的新宿线？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:21.27,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,也存在我们跳跃到了其它世界线的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:23.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们真能平安回到吾野吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:23.96,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我也想问
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.33,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,喂 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:28.02,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,为什么要取远地点号这个名字呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:28.66,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:31.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:32.45,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:35.09,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这么说来 静留会起这种名字确实很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:36.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,毕竟这是专业术语
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:37.05,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:38.26,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:48.71,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,因为远地点是月球离地球最遥远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.82,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在那之后 就只会不断靠近了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Signs_WText,Sign,0,0,0,,本视频由S1百综字幕组汉化\N仅供学习交流,严禁用于商业用途,请于24小时内删除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.94,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,这条铁路是毒太郎新线\N该铁路只围绕池袋运行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:10.92,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,黑木的指哨声采取的是\N吹乌野豌豆的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:17.67,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,这是二战时波兰的勇敢号装甲列车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:26.36,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,{\an7}浑沌的UFO是第二代\N初代因为椎名町的影响而消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.71,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,吾野柔术中有类似于摔角的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.47,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,叶香根本没有读过涩泽龙彦的书所以没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:28.17,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,该建筑物内部分为三个空间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:35.36,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,第一个空间出自叶香想象中的宇宙和铁路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:05.97,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,第二个空间是池袋站北端的杂司谷隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:46.77,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,第三个空间是Sunshine水族馆\N位于SunshineCity顶楼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.80,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,星空变化自位于SunshineCity顶楼的\N柯尼卡美能达天文馆「满天」\N和之前的水族馆在同一楼\N都是MyGO中水族馆、天象馆的原型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:47.27,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,这里的瀑布变化自\NSunshine City的喷水广场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:48.39,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,监督水岛努认为\N已发生的事情是无法复原的\N说出口的话无法抹消也无法视而不见\N但却可以修复
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:50.40,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,此处重复的大楼是Sunshine 60\N建于原巢鸭监狱的空地上\N不止这么多栋，只是画面上放不下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:10.67,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,虽然仙人飒爽地离去了\N但水流的尽头似乎是万丈深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:21.70,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,乌鸦飞回东长崎方向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:34.08,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,监督认为吾野最奇妙之处在于\N无论其他人是什么样子\N所有人都能自然地接受\N仿佛什么事都没发生一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:43.84,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,诚老师7G时是正常时的1/6\N现在是正常时的1.6倍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:12.62,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,监督表示：「大家都说那是西武新宿线，真是这样吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:22:00.90,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,優しい人のなり方を 誰か教えてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:08.38,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,頼れる人のなり方を 誰か教えてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:27.38,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,雨に濡れて傘も差せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.29,0:22:31.11,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,いることもどうでもよくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:34.91,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,明るさが急に怖くなって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:39.18,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,大丈夫じゃないよ 大丈夫じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:43.41,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,一緒に歩くの嫌になって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:47.38,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,でもひとりでいたいわけじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:51.08,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,目を合わせて笑えなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.66,0:22:56.43,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,大丈夫じゃない それは大丈夫じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:23:01.31,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,何度 傷つけ 間違って 失敗して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:05.78,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,優しさ蔑ろにしただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:09.38,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,傷ついて 許して 許されて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:13.16,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,お前は生きろと言われただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:17.08,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,みんなひとりぼっちだけど 孤独だけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:20.99,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,あなただけここにいれば 孤独じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:22:00.90,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,多希望有人能告诉我 如何成为一个温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:08.38,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,多希望有人能告诉我 如何成为一个可靠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:27.38,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,任由雨水打湿自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.29,0:22:31.11,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,也无所谓撑不撑伞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:34.91,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,突然对光明感到恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:39.18,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我很不安啊 我很不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:43.41,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,变得讨厌与他人并肩而行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:47.38,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,但又并非是想要孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:51.08,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我们视线相交 却无法展露笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.66,0:22:56.43,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我很不安啊 这很不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:23:01.31,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我无数次伤害你 误会你 犯下错误
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:05.78,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,那都是因为我忽视了你的温柔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:09.38,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我受到伤害 宽恕他人 被他人谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:13.16,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,这都是因为你曾鼓励我活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:17.08,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,虽然大家形单影只 但这绝非孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:20.99,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,只要你仍身处此地 这便不是孤独
